Hereâ€™s a sample POST request that uses the password query parameter to change the password for the system-level user account with the username lgreen to End321!. The request is made using a system-level user account that includes the security role. https://docs.hitachivantara.com/internal/api/webapp/print/72cda581-a515-4975-93dd-f591140b46a3

